reviews.review_text: Very Average No Highlights, keep moving

best capture of this show lots of choices for this show (sbd, matrix, FM master) but this healy ultramatrix is my fav. Less roomy than the matrix or FM master and more lively and with better soundstage than the sbd. I'm not usually a big fan of the 80's ultramatrix because they have too much of the mics mixed in and you have to listen really loud to feel any punch. This night they got a good mix.
